---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 66
  - Title: Dîvâni Shamsi Tabriz
    Location: XLVIII
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=Snares of the Soul
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Snare of Woman
---
Thou wert a favourite falcon, kept in captivity by an old woman：
When thou heard’st the falcon-drum thou didst fly away into the Void.
